Support end-users feedback channels and provide solutions to optimize the product strategies;
Cooperate with Operations team and Product team to perform data analysis and reports.
Requirements:

Degree holder in Computer Science / Statistics / Information Technology or related discipline;
3+ years of experience in data analysis, preferably in Finance or IT industry;
Hands-on experience in data analytical tools including Tableau, Microsoft Power BI, Cognos, etc.;
Strong business sense, able to discover problems from data and capture opportunities;
Good logical and analytical skills, able to work under pressure;
Candidate with solid management experience can apply Business Intelligence Manager role;
Fluent in speaking Cantonese, English and Mandarin.
