Job Descriptions


This position is to support ensuring master data integrity in core operational system for freight forwarding business as well as managing the process to keep and improve data integrity and quality both from viewpoint of operational efficiency and Data Analytic.  Expected to work under the supervision of Manager in charge of master data.



üPerform daily master data maintenance tasks in global operational system;
üSupport preparing rule or guideline related to master data;

üMonitor and verify master data quality and take a necessary counter action;

üSupport planning and executing improvement on master data maintenance process and model fitting to data analytic or operational purpose;

ü Communicate with regions and countries about master data maintenance issue.
Qualification & experience Requirements:-

Experience and knowledge of operation in air or ocean freight forwarding is great advantage;
Preferable to have some working experiences as an office worker, but fresh graduate without experience can be considered as well;
Ability to work on own initiative within agreed boundaries;
Degree holder or above in related discipline;
Good communication and writing skill in English, particularly for preparing a manual, SOP and/or any other documentation;
Experience and knowledge of freight forwarding operating system (particularly CargoWise One) is great advantage;
Experience and knowledge to manage master data in any type of system is great advantage;
Immediately available preferred. 

Interested parties please send full resume with employment history and expected salary to HRA Division, Yusen Logistics Global Management Limited at Level 31, Tower 1, Kowloon Commerce Centre, 51 Kwai Cheong Road, Kwai Chung or by email to hr.ylhk @ hk.yusen-logistics.com.

